        <section id="uses-comp">
            <h>complement</h>
            <p>Like many adjectives, <g>trang</g> can be used as the complement of the
                adverbialising particle <a href="?gd=gu"><g>gu</g></a> – <g>gu trang</g>
                <en>busily</en>.</p>
            <p><xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Calum sgìth – tha e ag obair <m>gu trang</m> anns an achadh.</gd>
                        <tr>Malcolm is tired – he is working busily in the field.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </section>
